<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink304">
<l>kallāk kōvalar kōliṟ ṟōṇṭiya</l>
<l>vāṉīrp pattal yāṉai vauvuṅ</l>
<l>kallatark kavalai celliṉ melliyaṟ</l>
<l>puyaṉeṭuṅ kūntal pulampum</l>
<l>vayamāṉ ṟōṉṟal vallā tīmē</l>
      </lg>
 <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>If you go to the crossroad of  stony paths,</l>
<l>where elephant steals [water] from cows’ water pit </l>
<l>dug with sticks by the unlearned cowherds,</l>
<l>the tender-natured [girl] with long tresses,</l>
<l>[as dark as] a cloud,</l> 
<l>will suffer alone.</l> 
<l>O great man with strong horses! Do not dare! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
